          <p class="text-gray-700">Most brand agencies: Start with Framer ($1,500, DIY build). Upgrade to Webflow custom site when hitting $500K+ annual revenue. Prism Brand Studio invested $8,400 in Webflow site, saw revenue increase $1.2M first year (143x ROI). Professional website pays for itself with one $25K project. Don't cut corners - your website is your primary sales tool. Budget accordingly.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="border-[3px] border-fuchsia-200 p-6">
