          <p class="text-gray-700">Process section must include: Phases ("Discovery, Strategy, Design, Launch"), timeline per phase ("Discovery: 2 weeks"), deliverables per phase ("Strategy: Brand platform, positioning, messaging"), team involved ("Creative Director leads Strategy phase"), client involvement ("Weekly check-ins, 2 approval milestones"). Visualize process (timeline graphic, flowchart, animated scroll revealing phases). Demystify your work. Clients hire experts they understand. Hide your process, lose the project.</p>
